text: Callipogonius hircinus is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Henry Walter Bates in 1885. It is known from Honduras and Mexico.BioLib.cz - Callipogonius hircinus. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Pogonocherini Category:Beetles described in 1885
